      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The still photograph shows a young woman with a plait pigtail and traditional clothing looking past the camera into the foreground. Men in traditional clothing are seen in the background.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">‘Tana’ was the first Albanian feature film to be shot independently. It was directed by Kristaq Dhamo, produced by company ‘Shqipëria e Re’ and released in 1958.</ab>
